body: Nightcrawler guessed with Spidey with Colossus and Wolverine in tow for a handful of panels. It gave one of the group’s original creators, Len Wein, an opportunity to fill his babies’ word balloons for a two-issue adventure. The Amazing Spider-Man #161, Oct 1976. Writer Len Wein; artists Ross Andru and Mike Esposito.
